	Removed the makedepends to pkg-config (part of base-devel)

	* 2.2.11-5 :

	Realized that afterstep doesn't like x86_64 compilation (random files was lacking in the package). Fixed using -j1.

	* 2.2.11-4 :

	Compilation for libpng16.

